WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: RYkVaE9wzQE

NOTE Language: en

00:01:14.140 --> 00:01:18.980
The other day I talked to you about

00:01:19.186 --> 00:01:24.706
the importance of dedication in Sahaja Yoga

00:01:24.947 --> 00:01:29.107
and the devotion that one should have.

00:01:30.380 --> 00:01:35.660
Actually, when we are close to the mountain,

00:01:35.860 --> 00:01:38.660
we can’t see much of it,

00:01:38.900 --> 00:01:42.340
and that’s why we don’t realize

00:01:42.780 --> 00:01:46.820
the volume that is so close to us,

00:01:47.100 --> 00:01:50.820
the greatness that is facing us.

00:01:56.020 --> 00:01:58.820
This is one of the illusions that works out

00:01:59.020 --> 00:02:04.940
for people who do not realize it mentally —

00:02:05.260 --> 00:02:07.820
what they are in for,

00:02:08.100 --> 00:02:10.380
where are they, what have they found,

00:02:10.620 --> 00:02:13.820
what is Self-realization, what is its magnitude,

00:02:14.060 --> 00:02:16.980
how far they have to go,

00:02:18.980 --> 00:02:23.580
why are they chosen, what is their purpose of life,

00:02:23.940 --> 00:02:31.540
how far they have come up, how far they can understand.

00:02:31.860 --> 00:02:36.140
All these things are beyond the grasp,

00:02:36.340 --> 00:02:40.180
and one gets stunned, one doesn’t know

00:02:40.420 --> 00:02:46.060
what has happened to him when he got Realization actually.

00:02:49.180 --> 00:02:54.660
That’s why to understand this is only possible

00:02:54.900 --> 00:02:59.420
if you can understand how to dedicate,

00:02:59.700 --> 00:03:02.780
how to devote yourself.

00:03:03.260 --> 00:03:06.380
If you want to analyze anything

00:03:06.620 --> 00:03:10.900
on the basis of your rationality, you are too stunned.

00:03:11.140 --> 00:03:13.900
It’s too beyond you. It’s fantastic.

00:03:14.140 --> 00:03:17.100
It is too much. It’s really beyond you.

00:03:17.340 --> 00:03:20.980
Now think of it — you have got Realization. Can you believe it?

00:03:21.260 --> 00:03:23.300
That you can, in your life time…

00:03:23.540 --> 00:03:26.980
if somebody had told you this, you would never have believed it —

00:03:27.220 --> 00:03:30.700
that how can you get your Realization in this earth?

00:03:30.940 --> 00:03:32.140
Of course you were seeking —

00:03:32.340 --> 00:03:34.100
because people were saying we have to seek,

00:03:34.300 --> 00:03:35.580
also you felt you have to seek —

00:03:35.780 --> 00:03:39.260
but you never thought that this will materialize like this,

00:03:39.460 --> 00:03:41.020
that you will get your Realization.

00:03:41.220 --> 00:03:46.940
Then, after getting Realization, you could not feel what it was.

00:03:47.220 --> 00:03:49.140
Just if you have dropped into the ocean,

00:03:49.340 --> 00:03:52.460
and you don’t know what is the dimension of this ocean.

00:03:52.780 --> 00:03:54.900
How far you have gone into it?

00:03:55.180 --> 00:04:00.060
What is it? Where are we? What is our purpose?

00:04:00.340 --> 00:04:04.260
To add up to all the mess, we become thoughtless.

00:04:06.620 --> 00:04:14.620
So you cannot even find out as to, rationally, what it is.

00:04:14.820 --> 00:04:19.980
So, the immensity of this experience,

00:04:21.900 --> 00:04:27.860
the glory of your Mother’s coming,

00:04:29.060 --> 00:04:32.460
or the precious gift of your Self-realization —

00:04:32.700 --> 00:04:36.660
nothing can be realized through your understanding.

00:04:36.860 --> 00:04:40.420
Try to think — what have you got?

00:04:40.660 --> 00:04:43.420
Can you measure it with your understanding?

00:04:43.660 --> 00:04:47.100
Can you understand what has happened?

00:04:47.380 --> 00:04:49.300
No, you cannot.

00:04:49.580 --> 00:04:51.660
Because rationality cannot give you

00:04:51.860 --> 00:04:55.660
the dimensions into which you have fallen.

00:04:56.100 --> 00:04:59.620
The rationality is actually broken out.

00:04:59.860 --> 00:05:02.180
There is no rationality left now anymore

00:05:02.500 --> 00:05:06.500
to even communicate as to what you have been

00:05:06.780 --> 00:05:09.220
seeking and where have you landed.

00:05:09.540 --> 00:05:13.780
So the only method you have got now —

00:05:13.980 --> 00:05:15.780
or only way is left to you —

00:05:16.060 --> 00:05:18.820
for a drop which has become an ocean,

00:05:19.060 --> 00:05:21.180
is to dissolve more in the ocean,

00:05:21.380 --> 00:05:24.980
so that you feel the ocean at least.

00:05:25.380 --> 00:05:27.580
And to communicate with other drops

00:05:27.820 --> 00:05:32.980
in such a way that you know the whole through all of them.

00:05:36.420 --> 00:05:42.380
So first is a complete devotion. It’s very important.

00:05:43.060 --> 00:05:47.220
In this incarnation only it is so very important —

00:05:47.460 --> 00:05:50.540
because you have got Realization.

00:05:50.860 --> 00:05:53.260
If you did not have Realization — all right.

00:05:53.500 --> 00:05:58.140
Murmuring souls — all right. Half-baked people — all right.

00:05:58.420 --> 00:06:01.300
Little bit misbehaving — all right.

00:06:01.620 --> 00:06:06.860
This can be forgiven, that can be forgiven… everything is forgiven.

00:06:07.060 --> 00:06:11.620
To look at it, everybody thinks that “Mother is forgiving us.”

00:06:11.940 --> 00:06:14.340
But that’s not the point.

00:06:14.620 --> 00:06:19.220
I am forgiving because of My own nature.

00:06:19.620 --> 00:06:22.180
But you do not take it for granted.

00:06:22.420 --> 00:06:26.900
You are harming yourself by accepting that forgiveness.

00:06:27.180 --> 00:06:28.180
If you all the time think,

00:06:28.420 --> 00:06:30.700
“O Mother, You are so forgiving, please forgive me”…

00:06:30.900 --> 00:06:32.220
you are already forgiven, as it is.

00:06:32.420 --> 00:06:34.020
Once you call Me “Mother”, you’re forgiven.

00:06:34.260 --> 00:06:36.100
But what’s the advantage?

00:06:36.340 --> 00:06:38.860
You don’t have any advantage out of it.

00:06:39.100 --> 00:06:41.140
You are a loser.

00:06:41.420 --> 00:06:46.060
And this point at least rationally if you understand,

00:06:46.340 --> 00:06:51.980
then you will understand what is a devotion.

00:06:53.860 --> 00:07:01.020
So, in devotion of Sahaja Yoga, one has to realize

00:07:01.300 --> 00:07:05.220
that the things that are in Sahaja Yoga,

00:07:05.420 --> 00:07:06.780
that you have seen in Sahaja Yoga,

00:07:06.980 --> 00:07:09.340
are beyond your mind — first thing.

00:07:09.580 --> 00:07:12.100
Definitely, they are beyond human conception.

00:07:12.380 --> 00:07:14.820
So, on human level, you do not discuss them,

00:07:15.060 --> 00:07:17.220
and you do not talk about them.

00:07:17.500 --> 00:07:23.380
But on the collective level you can talk.

00:07:24.180 --> 00:07:27.100
And when you come to the collective level,

00:07:27.420 --> 00:07:29.100
then you have to understand

00:07:29.340 --> 00:07:34.140
that relationship with Me is more established, better established

00:07:34.380 --> 00:07:39.260
if you establish your relationships with others,

00:07:39.460 --> 00:07:42.820
in a very collective and homogeneous way.

00:07:43.060 --> 00:07:45.900
As I told you, the drop becomes the ocean;

00:07:46.140 --> 00:07:47.980
and the drop has to become the ocean

00:07:48.180 --> 00:07:52.020
by dissolving all its “dropness”

00:07:53.740 --> 00:07:55.540
with other drops.

00:07:55.740 --> 00:07:58.940
And all the drops dropping their dropness

00:07:59.140 --> 00:08:02.140
become the ocean ultimately.

00:08:02.380 --> 00:08:05.980
So we’ll see that devotion is double-wedged:

00:08:06.220 --> 00:08:11.020
one is to each other, and one is to your Mother.

00:08:11.262 --> 00:08:16.942
So the devotion to Me means actually facing to yourself.

00:08:17.222 --> 00:08:19.382
You face yourself first of all,

00:08:19.622 --> 00:08:23.702
and see for yourself what are you doing.

00:08:23.942 --> 00:08:27.182
You are your own enemy; nobody is your enemy.

00:08:27.462 --> 00:08:33.062
Your Mother is not, definitely. She’s not your enemy by any chance.

00:08:33.302 --> 00:08:36.542
And no bhoots are your enemies — in the way,

00:08:36.782 --> 00:08:40.262
if you do not allow them, they can’t be there.

00:08:41.502 --> 00:08:43.182
No evil person is your enemy,

00:08:43.382 --> 00:08:48.902
because he cannot be effective if you are spiritually equipped.

00:08:49.182 --> 00:08:53.622
So you are your own enemy, is decided now.

00:08:54.462 --> 00:08:58.342
The only way to get rid of that enemy of yours -

00:08:58.542 --> 00:09:00.102
you have to dedicate.

00:09:00.382 --> 00:09:03.662
Supposing you say

00:09:03.942 --> 00:09:09.862
that “I have faith in Mother,” or “in God.”

00:09:10.862 --> 00:09:13.702
So you are holding on to something, isn’t it?

00:09:13.942 --> 00:09:16.022
And you are discarding something.

00:09:16.302 --> 00:09:18.822
But this hold has to be very strong.

00:09:19.022 --> 00:09:21.702
Rationally, if you at that time when you are sinking,

00:09:21.942 --> 00:09:24.662
will you rationalize, “Whether I should hold the hand

00:09:24.862 --> 00:09:27.462
of this person who is saving, is correct or not?”

00:09:27.702 --> 00:09:31.142
No, you’ll just… your grip will be very strong.

00:09:31.422 --> 00:09:32.582
It will be extremely strong,

00:09:32.782 --> 00:09:35.942
and you will grip it with full force, with full faith —

00:09:36.182 --> 00:09:39.302
that “Some or other, save me!”

00:09:40.622 --> 00:09:44.702
And that kind of a feeling should be within us

00:09:44.982 --> 00:09:50.982
that “I am a person who is sinking because of myself.

00:09:51.702 --> 00:09:58.382
And if I am to be saved, I have to be absolutely,

00:09:58.582 --> 00:10:03.622
completely submerged in Sahaja Yoga.

00:10:04.222 --> 00:10:07.982
Absolutely I have to become one with it,

00:10:08.262 --> 00:10:09.742
then only I can be saved.”

00:10:09.982 --> 00:10:11.302
Because at this level,

00:10:11.502 --> 00:10:15.462
where you are realized souls of a higher level…

00:10:15.662 --> 00:10:20.862
now for a next jump, as I was saying to you — is devotion.

00:10:21.062 --> 00:10:26.222
Anything else has to be secondary, under the circumstances.

00:10:26.462 --> 00:10:29.102
If it is primary

00:10:29.342 --> 00:10:33.102
and your attention is still on that,

00:10:33.742 --> 00:10:35.742
then you cannot have this second jump.

00:10:35.942 --> 00:10:38.742
First jump you have already done, you have got your Realization.

00:10:39.022 --> 00:10:42.382
But from first jump to second jump —

00:10:42.622 --> 00:10:45.342
you’ve worked hard, you have come to the second jump —

00:10:45.582 --> 00:10:49.702
in the second jump, you have to face it up.

00:10:50.062 --> 00:10:52.582
You should not feel disgusted with yourself

00:10:52.782 --> 00:10:54.862
nor dejected with yourself for nothing.

00:10:55.062 --> 00:10:59.102
But treat yourself as a separate entity.

00:10:59.742 --> 00:11:02.942
And dedication is, actually, turning back to yourself

00:11:03.142 --> 00:11:05.022
and looking forward

00:11:05.302 --> 00:11:10.582
towards the divine personality in you.

00:11:10.822 --> 00:11:12.902
Once there is divine personality in you,

00:11:13.182 --> 00:11:15.022
there’s no problem of devotion.

00:11:15.262 --> 00:11:20.382
You’ll just become one with it; you’ll start enjoying it.

00:11:20.982 --> 00:11:24.262
But this rationality is the worst thing,

00:11:24.462 --> 00:11:26.142
that plays tricks with you,

00:11:26.422 --> 00:11:29.742
which deviates you from understanding

00:11:30.022 --> 00:11:33.142
that whatever life you have led so far

00:11:33.422 --> 00:11:36.822
has been on a very material, gross life.

00:11:37.102 --> 00:11:41.702
You came out of it, you have grown out of it, you have come up.

00:11:41.942 --> 00:11:48.542
Now, to blossom, to become fragrant,

00:11:50.142 --> 00:11:54.942
you have to give up rationality. That’s a binding [POINT?].

00:11:57.419 --> 00:11:59.298
You have to be yourself, that’s all.

00:11:59.379 --> 00:12:03.739
We should not be our own enemies. Are we?

00:12:04.059 --> 00:12:07.299
So, once you start facing yourself, you will like yourself.

00:12:07.539 --> 00:12:08.939
You won’t feel disgusted.

00:12:09.139 --> 00:12:11.339
Because that what “yourself” I’m talking about

00:12:11.579 --> 00:12:13.979
is glorious, is beautiful,

00:12:14.179 --> 00:12:19.099
is without any kalanka [blemish] on that, is absolutely detached.

00:12:19.379 --> 00:12:23.339
But, first of all, your attention has to accept it —

00:12:23.579 --> 00:12:28.219
that “This detachment is my life; I’m a different personality now.

00:12:28.499 --> 00:12:32.659
Detachment is my nourishment.”

00:12:36.099 --> 00:12:37.659
Detach yourself.

00:12:39.025 --> 00:12:44.905
So, to develop that kind of understanding about the truth,

00:12:45.105 --> 00:12:51.025
first of all, you should absolutely fix yourself on the truth.

00:12:51.385 --> 00:12:54.185
And the truth is that you are the instrument of God,

00:12:54.425 --> 00:12:55.745
that you have got Realization,

00:12:55.985 --> 00:13:00.825
that you have got a special awareness,

00:13:01.105 --> 00:13:05.505
which people do not have. Stand on that.

00:13:06.305 --> 00:13:09.145
And proclaim it. You are not to be afraid of it.

00:13:09.345 --> 00:13:11.985
You have got Realization, no doubt. You have felt it.

00:13:12.225 --> 00:13:13.705
Say it: “I’ve got Realization.

00:13:13.945 --> 00:13:18.985
Nothing doing, I know I’m a realized soul.” Firm on that.

00:13:19.225 --> 00:13:23.665
In this expression of truth, you have to be like the light.

00:13:23.985 --> 00:13:26.305
The light asserts.

00:13:26.505 --> 00:13:30.705
It not only asserts but it shows others also that it shines.

00:13:30.945 --> 00:13:35.185
It shows others that “I am the light,”

00:13:35.425 --> 00:13:38.105
that “You walk in my light,

00:13:38.345 --> 00:13:42.745
and if you don’t try to do it, I may burn you.”

00:13:43.025 --> 00:13:46.945
So they have that… what you call, that…

00:13:47.665 --> 00:13:52.465
I don’t know what’s the word is… Tejasvita. Tejas.

00:13:53.105 --> 00:13:54.785
Sharpness of light.

00:13:55.065 --> 00:13:57.905
That tejasvita is there, that sharpness of light.

00:13:58.185 --> 00:14:00.825
That is the proof of your truth.

00:14:01.065 --> 00:14:02.905
You are not afraid of any prime minister,

00:14:03.105 --> 00:14:06.305
or any minister, or any king, or anyone.

00:14:06.505 --> 00:14:08.945
But — “This is the fact. That’s the thing.

00:14:09.145 --> 00:14:13.305
I know I am a realized soul, I am the truth.”

00:14:15.465 --> 00:14:18.585
If you say, “I’m the truth,” whatever you will say

00:14:18.825 --> 00:14:22.945
will be the truth, no doubt about it.

00:14:23.705 --> 00:14:27.465
Whatever you will do will be the truth. But say, “I’m the truth.”

00:14:27.785 --> 00:14:31.105
But for that, a real purification is needed

00:14:31.305 --> 00:14:35.585
about facing yourself fully, in dedication.

00:14:35.825 --> 00:14:37.905
Means you are holding on to your Mother,

00:14:38.145 --> 00:14:39.825
you are holding on to Sahaja Yoga,

00:14:40.065 --> 00:14:42.745
you are holding on to that truth which you have found out.

00:14:42.985 --> 00:14:45.465
And here you are facing others.

00:14:45.705 --> 00:14:49.425
Without that you cannot do it; your source is that.

00:14:50.265 --> 00:14:53.345
You are standing on the truth.

00:14:53.545 --> 00:14:59.505
And that is such a power, such a strength.

00:15:00.025 --> 00:15:02.185
All of them if you see — Christ had that power,

00:15:02.385 --> 00:15:04.905
Mohammed had that power — all these great people had that power

00:15:05.145 --> 00:15:10.825
to say the truth, with full courage,

00:15:11.065 --> 00:15:14.665
with that assertion that people will accept it.

00:15:14.905 --> 00:15:16.985
And they would suffer even for that, they wouldn’t mind.

00:15:17.225 --> 00:15:19.305
But whatever is the truth has to be said.

00:15:19.505 --> 00:15:23.625
That’s the first point one should know about dedication —

00:15:23.825 --> 00:15:26.185
that you are dedicated fully,

00:15:26.385 --> 00:15:29.585
that you are not afraid of anyone.

00:15:30.105 --> 00:15:34.225
You are not worried about your losses.

00:15:34.465 --> 00:15:36.225
Some people have lost their heads also,

00:15:36.465 --> 00:15:39.905
completely cut their heads. People have tortured them.

00:15:40.145 --> 00:15:43.065
Some people have been… taken away all their money,

00:15:43.265 --> 00:15:44.625
have been tortured in every way,

00:15:44.865 --> 00:15:47.025
but they thought this was the truth, they stood by it.

00:15:47.225 --> 00:15:50.065
Some of them were stupid fools; they stood for something

00:15:50.265 --> 00:15:51.985
that was not truth. They did.

00:15:52.225 --> 00:15:55.145
But now you know that you are standing on the truth,

00:15:55.345 --> 00:15:58.265
and for that, you should be willing to sacrifice anything —

00:15:58.465 --> 00:16:03.105
so-called sacrifice, because you are not sacrificing the truth.

00:16:03.505 --> 00:16:06.065
What you had tried sacrificing is untruth.

00:16:06.305 --> 00:16:09.345
For that, you require people of strength and courage,

00:16:09.585 --> 00:16:12.265
and not these half-baked people.

00:16:12.505 --> 00:16:13.825
You see, till morning till evening

00:16:14.025 --> 00:16:17.105
asking for forgiveness from Mother. What is it?

00:16:17.345 --> 00:16:18.945
What is there to ask for forgiveness —

00:16:19.185 --> 00:16:21.505
because I am forgiving you every moment.

00:16:21.745 --> 00:16:25.985
But what are you doing to yourself? What sort of a person you are?

00:16:27.745 --> 00:16:29.985
You think about it, that you have to stand on the truth.

00:16:30.185 --> 00:16:34.985
For that, you have to be a strong, courageous person

00:16:35.265 --> 00:16:38.505
with that sharpness, that tejasvita within you —

00:16:38.785 --> 00:16:41.825
of the light of the beacon.

00:16:42.385 --> 00:16:45.825
But at the same time, you have to have complete dedication.

00:16:46.025 --> 00:16:49.545
Supposing there is no oil in this — it will all go off.

00:16:49.745 --> 00:16:52.865
It has to have oil.

00:16:53.545 --> 00:16:55.105
It will go off.

00:16:55.305 --> 00:16:58.265
So the dedication part is the oil in you,

00:16:58.465 --> 00:17:03.345
is the attachment, complete attachment to your source.

00:17:03.625 --> 00:17:05.705
That’s the dedication.

00:17:05.945 --> 00:17:08.665
But that dedication should not give you

00:17:08.905 --> 00:17:14.865
any other ideas but of a light which shines,

00:17:16.305 --> 00:17:22.465
which corrects others, guides the path of other people.

00:17:22.705 --> 00:17:27.105
If that is not so, then the source that you are tapping

00:17:27.345 --> 00:17:29.465
is not coming to you fully,

00:17:29.705 --> 00:17:34.665
and that your light is not burning properly.

00:17:37.385 --> 00:17:41.265
So, into dedication when you go,

00:17:43.665 --> 00:17:48.345
you must not think that it is any surrendering —

00:17:48.545 --> 00:17:52.345
the so-called surrendering, that you become like a cabbage.

00:17:52.585 --> 00:17:55.385
That’s the idea people have — that you become like cabbage.

00:17:55.585 --> 00:17:59.225
But you become dynamic.

00:18:01.545 --> 00:18:05.265
You become real power —

00:18:06.505 --> 00:18:09.305
not of destruction but of construction.

00:18:09.545 --> 00:18:11.865
I mean, for destruction you don’t need much power.

00:18:12.145 --> 00:18:14.265
Only for construction you need power.

00:18:14.505 --> 00:18:17.225
For destruction how much do you need? Very little.

00:18:17.465 --> 00:18:19.665
You can destroy the whole thing in no time.

00:18:19.905 --> 00:18:28.305
But for the construction you really require great power.

00:18:28.505 --> 00:18:31.265
And that power — sustained power,

00:18:31.505 --> 00:18:34.385
or flowing power — has to be there.

00:18:34.625 --> 00:18:37.785
For that, dedication is needed.

00:18:38.065 --> 00:18:41.545
Holding on to your source of power,

00:18:41.785 --> 00:18:45.865
you have to stand firm, courageously,

00:18:46.185 --> 00:18:52.105
without any fear.

00:18:54.305 --> 00:18:57.065
That’s the truth.

00:18:57.305 --> 00:18:59.825
That’s the truth you have to achieve.

00:19:00.065 --> 00:19:02.065
That’s very important.

00:19:02.305 --> 00:19:06.665
But this is only one side of the story.

00:19:06.985 --> 00:19:11.545
That’s not sufficient. Just being the truth,

00:19:11.905 --> 00:19:16.505
the aspect of one side is there.

00:19:16.825 --> 00:19:19.265
But the other side of it is

00:19:19.545 --> 00:19:25.505
that when this source comes to you, you become the compassion.

00:19:26.145 --> 00:19:28.665
The truth and the compassion are one thing.

00:19:28.905 --> 00:19:31.145
You won’t believe, but it is so.

00:19:31.385 --> 00:19:37.345
Like the wick and the oil combine to form the light.

00:19:38.025 --> 00:19:42.705
It is the burning of the oil gives you the light.

00:19:42.945 --> 00:19:48.065
In the same way, the compassion gives you the truth.

00:19:48.305 --> 00:19:52.905
There’s no difference whatsoever. Only the state is different —

00:19:53.105 --> 00:19:56.585
that you cannot see the light, which is oil,

00:19:56.825 --> 00:20:00.425
and oil, which is burning.

00:20:01.265 --> 00:20:07.225
So compassion is the one which is the source,

00:20:07.665 --> 00:20:10.865
as well as your store.

00:20:11.185 --> 00:20:15.105
So, from the source of compassion,

00:20:15.585 --> 00:20:17.425
you get your compassion.

00:20:17.665 --> 00:20:21.825
You see, I have seen people — they want to have compassion from Me,

00:20:22.105 --> 00:20:24.505
they want that I should love them.

00:20:24.785 --> 00:20:28.865
But — reflect it back — do they love others like that?

00:20:29.105 --> 00:20:30.665
I have known people, they have…

00:20:30.865 --> 00:20:34.825
say, for one person says harsh thing to another,

00:20:35.105 --> 00:20:37.705
and comes and asks Me, “Mother, forgive me for that,”

00:20:37.945 --> 00:20:41.825
or does something harsh just for the whim of the mind.

00:20:42.065 --> 00:20:43.585
“Mother, forgive me.”

00:20:43.825 --> 00:20:47.865
But when you ask for that, I would like to know:

00:20:48.145 --> 00:20:51.585
have you given compassion to another person?

00:20:51.825 --> 00:20:54.345
Even after getting forgiveness from Me —

00:20:54.545 --> 00:20:58.985
that Source of forgiveness, that Source of compassion —

00:20:59.185 --> 00:21:01.465
have you given compassion to others?

00:21:01.785 --> 00:21:04.225
Have you been compassionate to others?

00:21:04.465 --> 00:21:07.585
You see, it should not be one-sided.

00:21:07.825 --> 00:21:11.425
If you are taking the advantage of My compassion,

00:21:11.665 --> 00:21:13.185
it should not be one-sided,

00:21:13.385 --> 00:21:16.745
that you use it for your own benefit and forget about it.

00:21:16.985 --> 00:21:21.905
Then you will never grow. You will never grow.

00:21:22.145 --> 00:21:27.065
If you have to grow, then you must store that compassion within you.

00:21:27.305 --> 00:21:29.865
Whatever compassion I’ve given you, love I’ve given you,

00:21:29.946 --> 00:21:35.530
you must store that within you — and give that back to others.